From: L. David Baron <dbaron@dbaron.org>

Use GatherURL in ParseNameSpaceRule and ParseImageRect, and rename GatherURL to ParseURLOrString for clarity.  (Bug 604179)

Note that this adds a missing UngetToken(), which affects the other
consumer of GatherURL, parsing of @import rules.

diff --git a/layout/style/nsCSSParser.cpp b/layout/style/nsCSSParser.cpp
